---

<Layout>
<div class="index-root">
	<h1 class="main-title">shoの活動日誌</h1>
	<p class="description">プロフィールを載せる、技術記事を書く、書評を書くなどをしていく予定です。</p>

	<section aria-labelledby="profile-heading" class="profile-section center-section align-left">
		<h2 id="profile-heading" class="section-title">プロフィール</h2>
		<nav class="profile-nav vertical-nav">
			<ul class="profile-list vertical-list align-list">
				<li><a class="profile-link simple-link" href="/tech-profile">技術系プロフィールを見る</a></li>
				<li><a class="profile-link simple-link" href="/personal-profile">非技術系プロフィールを見る</a></li>
			</ul>
		</nav>
	</section>

	<section aria-labelledby="blog-heading" class="blog-section center-section align-left">
		<h2 id="blog-heading" class="section-title">ブログ記事</h2>
		<nav class="blog-nav">
			<ul class="profile-list vertical-list align-list">
				<li><a class="profile-link simple-link" href="/blog/books">独学で役立ったおすすめ技術書・教材リスト</a></li>
			</ul>
		</nav>
	</section>
</div>
</Layout>
<style>
.index-root {
	min-height: 100vh;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	justify-content: flex-start;
}
.align-left {
	align-items: flex-start !important;
}
.align-list {
	align-items: flex-start !important;
	padding-left: 0 !important;
}
</style>
<style>
.profile-list li + li {
	padding-top: 0.18rem;
}
</style>

<style>
.main-title {
	text-align: center;
	font-size: 2.4rem;
	font-weight: 800;
	letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	padding-top: 2.5rem;
	padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
	color: #1e293b;
}
.blog-section .vertical-list {
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	gap: 0.5rem;
	width: 100%;
	padding: 0 0 0 0.5em;
	list-style: none;
	align-items: flex-start;
}
.description {
	text-align: center;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	color: #334155;
	padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.section-title {
	font-size: 1.3rem;
	font-weight: 700;
	color: #475569;
	padding-bottom: 0.2rem;
	padding-left: 0.5em;
	border-left: 4px solid #a5b4fc;
	margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	margin-top: 2rem;
}
.center-section {
	max-width: 600px;
	margin-left: auto;
	margin-right: auto;
	margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
	padding: 0.7rem 0 0.2rem 0;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: center;
}
.description {
	text-align: center;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	color: #334155;
	padding-bottom: 0.7rem;
}
.vertical-nav {
	width: 100%;
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	align-items: center;
}
.vertical-list {
	display: flex;
	flex-direction: column;
	width: 100%;
	padding: 0 0 0 0.5em;
	list-style: none;
	align-items: flex-start;
}
.simple-link {
	display: inline-block;
	color: #334155;
	background: none;
	font-weight: 500;
	font-size: 1.08rem;
	text-decoration: underline;
	border-radius: 0;
	padding: 0.1em 0.2em;
	box-shadow: none;
	transition: color 0.18s;
}
.simple-link:hover {
	color: #6366f1;
	background: none;
	text-decoration: underline;
}
